"Connect, pair, and transfer privately over USB." = "通过 USB 私密地连接、配对与传输。";
"Get connected" = "建立连接";
"Open DroidMatch on Android and enable Secure USB." = "在 Android 上打开 DroidMatch，并启用“安全 USB”。";
"Connect by USB, unlock Android, and approve the ADB prompt." = "通过 USB 连接并解锁 Android，然后批准 ADB 提示。";
"Refresh on Mac, choose the device, and compare the six-digit pairing code on both screens." = "在 Mac 上刷新并选择设备，然后核对两端显示的六位配对码。";
"Browse and transfer" = "浏览与传输";
"Use Files and Media after the secure session is ready." = "安全会话就绪后，可在“文件”和“媒体”中浏览内容。";
"Android permissions are checked live. Grant or reselect access on Android when asked." = "Android 权限会实时检查；需要时请在 Android 上授权或重新选择访问范围。";
"Use Transfers to pause, resume, retry, or review saved work." = "在“传输”中可以暂停、继续、重试或查看已保存的任务。";
"If something doesn’t work" = "遇到问题时";
"No device: check the data cable, unlock Android, approve ADB, then refresh." = "未发现设备：检查数据线，解锁 Android，批准 ADB，然后刷新。";
"Authentication failed: reopen Secure USB and a new two-minute pairing window on Android." = "认证失败：在 Android 上重新启用“安全 USB”，并开启新的两分钟配对窗口。";
"Interrupted transfer: reconnect the same Android device and review Transfers." = "传输中断：重新连接同一台 Android 设备，并查看“传输”。";
"Privacy by default" = "默认保护隐私";
"DroidMatch keeps transfers local over USB and binds ADB forwards to this Mac." = "DroidMatch 仅通过 USB 在本地传输，并把 ADB 转发限制在这台 Mac。";
"Hardware serials stay out of the interface and normal logs." = "硬件序列号不会进入界面和常规日志。";
"Pairing records stay in Keychain; opening Help never reads credentials or connects a device." = "配对记录保存在钥匙串中；打开帮助不会读取凭据，也不会连接设备。";
"Only an explicit device connection reads a saved pairing key. A macOS Keychain prompt authorizes that read; it is not an Apple signing request, and DroidMatch has no password field. A rebuilt local ad-hoc app may prompt again because macOS can treat its changed code signature as a new app identity." = "只有用户主动连接设备时才会读取已保存的配对密钥。macOS 钥匙串提示是在授权这次读取，不是 Apple 签名请求；DroidMatch 自身没有密码输入框。本地 ad-hoc App 重建后代码签名会变化，macOS 可能把它视为新的 App 身份并再次询问。";
